                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://apnews.com/article/immigrant-detention-warehouses-ice-trump-a4a71226409cd9fedc9aa5de5ec90654&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(AP) ICE begins to purchase warehouses, but some owners are backing out of deals&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
