&lt;h4&gt;What can you do this week?&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Join the Red Hat Resistance February 26, 2026 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7iEKMU_KPjc&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
