				&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://apnews.com/article/minneapolis-shootings-kristi-noem-ice-congress-add9ac7b90f5677621009e8a603c0141&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(AP) Homeland Security Secretary Kristi Noem faces rising calls for her firing or impeachment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
