                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.govtrack.us/posts/571/2026-01-26_probably-another-shutdown&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(GovTrack) Probably another shutdown&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
