&lt;section class=&quot;block info&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Keeping you informed...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Trump&#39;s dementia is getting worse  &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cy7mev35x2lo&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;image-right&quot; style=&quot;width:225px&quot;&gt;

    &lt;a href=&quot;/images/JsI76sSkU2-800.webp&quot; class=&quot;lightbox-link&quot; aria-haspopup=&quot;dialog&quot; style=&quot;cursor:zoom-in&quot;&gt;
      &lt;img class=&quot;img-lightbox&quot; alt=&quot;Dear Jonas: Considering your Country decided not to give me the Nobel Peace Prize for having stopped 8 wars PLUS, I no longer feel an obligation to think purely of Peace, although it will always be predominant, but can now think about what is good and proper for the United States of America. Denmark cannot protect that land from Russia or China, and why do they have a &#39;right of ownership&#39; anyway? There are no written documents, it&#39;s only that a boat landed there hundreds of years ago, but we had boats landing there, also. I have done more for NATO than any other person since its founding, and now, NATO should do something for the United States. The World is not secure unless we have Complete and Total Control of Greenland. Thank you! President DJT&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; style=&quot;--img-width:200&quot; src=&quot;/images/JsI76sSkU2-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; height=&quot;887&quot; srcset=&quot;/images/JsI76sSkU2-200.webp 200w, /images/JsI76sSkU2-800.webp 800w&quot; sizes=&quot;200px&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;

        &lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Donny 2-Dolls has never been smart. His rambling, incoherent rants have become so common in his two terms as President that nobody really talks about them anymore. While his messages continue to reflect his stupidity, recent messages also point to something far worse. The president of the United States is in very serious (and obvious) cognitive decline. In one of his recent ramblings, he sent a letter to the Prime Minister of Norway threatening to take Greenland (A territory of Denmark) by military force because he wasn&#39;t awarded the Nobel Peace Prize (which is not awarded by the Norwegian government anyway, but by an independent committee).&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Ty Cobb, a former White House lawyer in Trump&#39;s first term, recently commented, &quot;I don&#39;t think there&#39;s anybody outside of the United States who believes that Trump is sane.&quot; Cobb pointed out that Trump&#39;s signs of dementia and cognitive decline are &quot;palpable.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;This has led many people to call for the invocation of the &lt;a href=&quot;/charters-of-freedom/constitution/#Amd25S4&quot;&gt;25th Amendment&lt;/a&gt;, which allows the vice president to assume the powers and duties of the president if the president is unable to discharge the duties of the office. Since J.D. Vance is nothing more than a Trump regime bootlicker, it&#39;s unlikely that any of the disasters Donny 2-Dolls has brought down on this country would be averted, but at the very least, we would no longer be led by a mentally unstable narcissist.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;blockquote&gt;
			&lt;p&gt;Dear Jonas: Considering your Country decided not to give me the Nobel Peace Prize for having stopped 8 wars PLUS, I no longer feel an obligation to think purely of Peace, although it will always be predominant, but can now think about what is good and proper for the United States of America. Denmark cannot protect that land from Russia or China, and why do they have a &#39;right of ownership&#39; anyway? There are no written documents, it&#39;s only that a boat landed there hundreds of years ago, but we had boats landing there, also. I have done more for NATO than any other person since its founding, and now, NATO should do something for the United States. The World is not secure unless we have Complete and Total Control of Greenland. Thank you! President DJT&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;figcaption class=&quot;blockquote-footer&quot;&gt;Donny 2-Dolls, American Dictator&lt;/figcaption&gt;
		&lt;/blockquote&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Related Links:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;ul class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cy7mev35x2lo&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(BBC) Trump ties Greenland demands to Nobel Prize in message to Norway leader&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.dailykos.com/stories/2026/1/19/2364242/-Trump-s-Greenland-letter-to-Norway-s-PM-is-insane-even-by-his-standards-how-deep-is-his-dementia&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(Daily KOS) Trump&#39;s Greenland letter to Norway&#39;s PM is insane even by his standards; how deep is his dementia?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FQfMx0Kfx98&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(YouTube-MS Now) Spiral! Mental decline, losing Nobel, &quot;Iceland&quot; debacle: Trump slumps amid Epstein, ICE revolt&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
