&lt;section&gt;
    &lt;p class=&quot;tangerine&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center;font-size:4em;padding:1.2rem 0px;&quot;&gt;Impeach. Convict. Remove.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Recap of this week in the revolution: Judge limits ICE-stapo violence against peaceful protesters. The Trump regime&amp;#39;s plan to undermine and then dismantle public education. Reporter reveals sloppy ICE-stapo recruitment process. Who&amp;#39;s next on our national hit list?&lt;/p&gt;
