&lt;section&gt;
    &lt;p class=&quot;tangerine&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center;font-size:4em;padding:1.2rem 0px;&quot;&gt;Impeach. Convict. Remove.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Recap of this week in the revolution: Trump regime returns National Guard control to states and Congress releases Jack Smith deposition. DeSantis misuses Florida taxpayer funds. Trump regime illegally abducts President Maduro and seizes Venezuela.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;

&lt;section class=&quot;block the-good&quot;&gt;
	&lt;h4&gt;The good...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Trump regime gives up its attempts to keep control of the National Guard in LA, Portland, and Chicago &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.latimes.com/politics/story/2025-12-31/trump-administration-retreats-in-newsom-lawsuit-over-national-guard-deployment&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;image-right&quot; style=&quot;width:225px&quot;&gt;

    &lt;a href=&quot;/images/ENum8eKori-800.webp&quot; class=&quot;lightbox-link&quot; aria-haspopup=&quot;dialog&quot; style=&quot;cursor:zoom-in&quot;&gt;
      &lt;img class=&quot;img-lightbox&quot; alt=&quot;California National Guard facing off against protesters&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; style=&quot;--img-width:200&quot; src=&quot;/images/ENum8eKori-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; height=&quot;408&quot; srcset=&quot;/images/ENum8eKori-200.webp 200w, /images/ENum8eKori-800.webp 800w&quot; sizes=&quot;200px&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;

            &lt;p class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;California National Guard facing off against protesters, June 9, 2025.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The Trump regime has been unable to come up with a compelling legal justification for deploying National Guard troops in California, Oregon, and Illinois. After 6 months of failed legal battles, the regime has finally given up its attempts to appeal court rulings ordering the removal of troops, effectively returning control of the National Guard to state leaders...where it has always belonged.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;blockquote&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;For six months, California National Guard troops have been used as political pawns by a President desperate to be king.&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;From the political display in MacArthur Park to their unlawful participation in indiscriminate immigration raids, the militaristic deployment of National Guard troops to Los Angeles streets has left lasting scars in Angeleno communities. There is a reason our founders decided military and civilian affairs must be kept separate; a reason that our military is, by design, apolitical.&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;figcaption class=&quot;blockquote-footer&quot;&gt;California Attorney General Rob Bonta&lt;/figcaption&gt;
        &lt;/blockquote&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Related Links:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;ul class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.latimes.com/politics/story/2025-12-31/trump-administration-retreats-in-newsom-lawsuit-over-national-guard-deployment&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(LA Times) Trump administration retreats in Newsom lawsuit over National Guard deployment&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://apnews.com/article/trump-national-guard-withdrawal-cities-6b7b02b832b24e17e6db483eb6c74425&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(AP) Trump says he&#39;s dropping push for National Guard in Chicago, LA and Portland, Oregon, for now&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;hr style=&quot;clear:both&quot;/&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Jack Smith deposition online &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gGtlalhdL4c&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Jack Smith testified to Congress that Donald Trump was responsible for the January 6 Capitol riot, and defended efforts to hold him accountable. The deposition and official transcript have both been released to the public and are available online.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Smith led a 2023 investigation into Trump&#39;s role in the events of January 6, 2021, and his retention of classified documents in his private residence after leaving office in 2021. He dropped the investigation after Trump&#39;s election as president in 2024 because the Justice Department does not allow indictments of a sitting president. But Smith testified that his investigation had gathered proof &quot;beyond a reasonable doubt&quot; that Trump had &quot;engaged in a criminal scheme&quot; to overturn the 2020 election.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;
			&lt;iframe width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/gGtlalhdL4c?si=8-3gxljk-57U_5lX&quot; title=&quot;YouTube video player&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allow=&quot;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;strict-origin-when-cross-origin&quot; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
		&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Related Links:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;ul class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2025/12/31/jack-smith-donald-trump-house-judiciary-committee-transcript/87976781007/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(USA Today) Trump &quot;caused&quot; Jan. 6 Capital riot, Jack Smith testified to Congress&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gGtlalhdL4c&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(YouTube-PBS NewsHour) Jack Smith deposition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
