&lt;/section&gt;

&lt;section class=&quot;block the-bad&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;The bad...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Florida governor misappropriates taxpayer&#39;s money to defeat ballot initiatives &lt;a href=&quot;https://youtu.be/EM0uTojxLCM?si=_ql99JvZn2pNdV1b&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Florida Governor Ron DeSantis&#39; administration spent over $35 million in taxpayer funds that were allocated for child welfare and medical services for political consulting and advertising campaigns to oppose ballot initiatives he opposed.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;While the governor is entitled to his own political opinions, the use of public funds previously allocated to other purposes is a misuse of taxpayer funds and violates the principle of accountability in government. &lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Professor emeritus Kenneth Goodman, former director of medical ethics at the University of Miami declared the spending of child welfare funds on &quot;undermining the will of the voters&quot; amounts to &quot;corruption at the expense of children.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;div style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;
            &lt;iframe width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/EM0uTojxLCM?si=2Tz5TgdzoS7XhaDP&quot; title=&quot;YouTube video player&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allow=&quot;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;strict-origin-when-cross-origin&quot; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Related Links:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;ul class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://youtu.be/EM0uTojxLCM?si=_ql99JvZn2pNdV1b&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(YouTube-Katie Phang) DeSantis caught funneling $35 million away from Floridians&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.miamiherald.com/news/politics-government/state-politics/article313630394.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(Miami Herald) DeSantis admin diverted child welfare and medical funds for consultants, ads&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
