&lt;section class=&quot;block the-ugly&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;The ugly...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Trump regime seizes control of Venezuela in unconstitutional war &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/white-house/trump-venezuela-nicolas-maduro-strikes-run-country-transition-military-rcna252044&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;image-right&quot; style=&quot;width:225px&quot;&gt;

    &lt;a href=&quot;/images/jO4ArW-U23-800.webp&quot; class=&quot;lightbox-link&quot; aria-haspopup=&quot;dialog&quot; style=&quot;cursor:zoom-in&quot;&gt;
      &lt;img class=&quot;img-lightbox&quot; alt=&quot;Dictator Trump kidnaps Venezuelan leader&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; style=&quot;--img-width:200&quot; src=&quot;/images/jO4ArW-U23-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; height=&quot;1000&quot; srcset=&quot;/images/jO4ArW-U23-200.webp 200w, /images/jO4ArW-U23-800.webp 800w&quot; sizes=&quot;200px&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;

            &lt;p class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;Image by &lt;a href=&quot;https://bsky.app/profile/50501movement.bsky.social/post/3mbjzkjltps2g&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;50501: The People&#39;s Movement&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The Trump regime has escalated its undeclared war on Venezuela by capturing the president and declaring that the United States will govern Venezuela until there&#39;s a &quot;proper transition.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;There is no legal, moral, or constitutional justification for this action. It is an outrageous act of war taken against a sovereign nation in a pathetic attempt to assume control of Venezuela&#39;s vast oil reserves. The Trump regime is trying to cover our country&#39;s failing economy, domestic turmoil, and its own plummeting approval ratings by launching a war against a made-up enemy to distract the media and the public.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The United States has become a threat to the world&#39;s stability and peace. While the country has a long history of imperialistic actions, it has never before been so blatant in flaunting domestic and international law and abusing its power.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;I am a patriot and a veteran of the United States military, and I have never been ashamed to be an American...until now.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Related Links:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;ul class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;
