                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.aljazeera.com/news/liveblog/2026/1/3/live-loud-noises-heard-in-venezuelas-capital-amid-us-tensions&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(Al Jazeera) Live: Trump says US will run Venezuela after Maduro&#39;s &quot;capture&quot;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
