&lt;section class=&quot;block the-ugly&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;The ugly...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        U.S. citizenship for sale &lt;a href=&quot;https://apnews.com/article/trump-gold-card-website-live-us-visa-22edbd7e65d188bbf6c8ec1d5f78d11a&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;image-right&quot; style=&quot;width:225px&quot;&gt;
            &lt;img class=&quot;img-link&quot; alt=&quot;Gold ticket with the words &#39;Admit One&#39;&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; style=&quot;--img-width:200&quot; src=&quot;/images/Roj4Vl5-8L-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;100&quot;&gt;
            &lt;p class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;Image by &lt;a href=&quot;https://pixabay.com/users/openclipart-vectors-30363/?utm_source=link-attribution&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=image&amp;utm_content=576228&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;OpenClipart-Vectors&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=&quot;https://pixabay.com//?utm_source=link-attribution&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=image&amp;utm_content=576228&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Pixabay&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;While the Trump regime is actively engaged in rounding up and deporting hard-working immigrants and imposing ridiculous requirements on tourists entering the country, they are also making it clear that this level of persecution only applies to the poor. If you&#39;re rich enough, you can literally buy a golden ticket to gain access to everything the United States has to offer. The ticket entitles its owner to permanent legal residency in the United States and a streamlined path to citizenship.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Donny 2-Dolls said the program will result in &quot;somebody great coming into our country because we think these will be some tremendous people.&quot; This tells you everything you need to know about our current Idiot in Chief. According to him, having money automatically makes a person &quot;tremendous,&quot; while poor people are expendable at best, and a nuisance to be eradicated at worst.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;When the idea was first released back in March, the Trump regime priced the cards at $5 million and estimated they would sell hundreds of thousands of the cards, raking in at least a trillion dollars. They&#39;ve lowered the price to a paltry $1 million, but are still expecting to earn billions of dollars from the program. And what do they plan to do with all this money they are going to be raking in? Donny 2-Dolls says the payments for these golden tickets will &quot;go to the U.S. government...where we can do things positive for the country.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Related Links:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;ul class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://apnews.com/article/trump-gold-card-website-live-us-visa-22edbd7e65d188bbf6c8ec1d5f78d11a&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(AP) Trump&#39;s &quot;gold card&quot; program goes live, offering US visas starting at $1 million per person&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2025/dec/10/tourists-social-media-trump&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(The Guardian) Tourists to US would have to reveal five years of social media activity under new Trump plan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;hr style=&quot;clear:both&quot;/&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        U.S. military seizes merchant oil tanker &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.npr.org/2025/12/11/g-s1-101668/seized-oil-tanker-off-the-coast-venezuela&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;image-right&quot; style=&quot;width:225px&quot;&gt;
            &lt;img class=&quot;img-link&quot; alt=&quot;Donny 2-Dolls receives a fake &#39;peace prize&#39; made up by the International Federation of Football Associations (FIFA)&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; style=&quot;--img-width:200&quot; src=&quot;/images/Znv8Yika1g-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;159&quot;&gt;
            &lt;p class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;While the United States is actively provoking a war with Venezuela, Donny 2-Dolls accepts a fake &quot;peace prize&quot; made up by the International Federation of Football Associations (FIFA).&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;The United States has seized a commercial oil tanker off the coast of Venezuela, and armed members of the Coast Guard boarded and took control of the ship by fast-roping off of helicopters hovering just off the deck of the ship.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Taking over a merchant ship outside our own coastal waters is unusual, and a violation of international law. The Trump regime is claiming the oil tanker is &quot;involved in an illicit oil shipping network supporting foreign terrorist organizations.&quot; As usual, they are not offering any evidence of their claims. The excuse is wearing a bit thin, as the regime has been labeling everything it opposes as terrorism. Immigrants residing in our country (legally or not) are being labeled terrorists. That was the case with Kilmar Abrego Garcia, who was deported and imprisoned due to a clerical error before the regime retroactively claimed, without evidence, he belonged to a terrorist organization. Venezuelan boats have been bombed in international waters, killing dozens of people who the regime is claiming, also without evidence, belong to narco-terrorist groups (Whatever that means). Now commercial oil tankers are being seized by our military using the same flimsy claims.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;The truth is, none of this has anything to do with terrorism or drug trafficking or defending the United States from imaginary threats. It is all about Trump&#39;s plan to overthrow Venezuelan president, Nicolás Maduro. Not because Maduro may have stolen the election in 2024, or because he is acting as a dictator, but because many of the Venezuelans whe have fled the country&#39;s political and economic situation have sought asylum (legally) in the United States. And let&#39;s not forget that Venezuela has the world&#39;s largest oil reserves, and the United States has a long history of fighting wars to control the international flow of oil. Trump has even stated that there is likely to be a ground invasion of Venezuela starting soon, though there is no reasonable legal justification for such an invasion of a sovereign nation.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Related Links:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;ul class=&quot;related-links&quot;&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.npr.org/2025/12/11/g-s1-101668/seized-oil-tanker-off-the-coast-venezuela&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(NPR) Trump says the U.S. has seized an oil tanker off the coast of Venezuela&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
				&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.dailykos.com/stories/2025/12/10/2357850/-Another-war-for-oil-US-seizes-tanker-off-Venezuela&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(Daily KOS) Another war for oil: US seizes tanker off Venezuela&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;hr style=&quot;clear:both&quot;/&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;


&lt;section class=&quot;block info&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Keeping you informed...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Retailers exploit your personal data to overcharge you using surveillance pricing &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-cbtUYshYM8&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;From airlines to groceries to rideshares to televisions, online shoppers are being exploited by surveillance pricing. Retailers use your private data, collecting all of your personal data together from all of your browser and mobile data points, to calculate the highest price you are willing to pay for a product or service, and then they charge that price. Meanwhile, the next person may be paying significantly less for the exact same product or service.&lt;/p&gt;
