                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-cbtUYshYM8&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(YouTube-Robert Reich and Inequality Media) The shady world of surveillance pricing (Ft. Lina Khan)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
