&lt;section class=&quot;block lighter-side&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;On the lighter side...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;
		&lt;a href=&quot;https://bsky.app/profile/decombest.bsky.social/post/3m6zqawky322n&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;
